summary: Do y'all know???? You can ship things that arent canon????? And you can ship things that aren't GOING to be canon??? You dont...
body:
Do y'all know???? You can ship things that arent canon????? And you can ship things that aren’t GOING to be canon??? You dont have to dislike people bc they like non-canon ships.

Also??? People are allowed to be wary about shipping tyrus bc they dont trust Disney especially after the shit they pulled with the Look Back.

Can we stop hating people bc of which guy they ship with Cyrus? I wanna not feel anxious every time I log onto Tumblr and see an Andi Mack post. Also? I ship both tyrus and jyrus at this point and I just don’t want to be scared people are gonna hate me bc I like either of them.
